<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_49_r1l4">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt Hıltpolt CƷiner vnd Andres </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r1l5">leͣber <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jn in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit herſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_line_1574191625857_269">vnd gepiete vormals etwieuil hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeẏ woꝛden 
<add><ab facs="#facs_49_line_1576653638800_2635">dıe in des hanſen </ab><ab facs="#facs_49_line_1576653642453_2640"><expan>Spangſteın<ex>er</ex>s</expan> ſloʒ </ab><ab facs="#facs_49_line_1576653645798_2645">gen Spangſtein ſey </ab><ab facs="#facs_49_line_1576653648516_2650"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
