<ab facs="#facs_49_r1l8">gnaden wol wiſʒentlıchen ſeẏ / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr durch vnſ<ex>er</ex>r <expan>wıllige<ex>n</ex></expan> </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r1l10">
<del rend="strikethrough">dinſte willen / von </del> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleuhtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r1l12">ewr hilff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>gnadıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiſen wöllet / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r1l13">willen / daʒ Jn dieſelb ir hab wider / oder aber gekeret werde / </ab>
