</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_49" id="23r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> von Osterreich </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fürgelegt Hiltpolt Cziner und Andres Leͣber, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz in in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        durchleuhtikeit, herschaft und gepiete vormals etwievil hab
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey worden, <add>die in des Hansen
                                    <expan>Spangstein<ex>er</ex>s</expan> sloz gen Spangstein sey
                                    <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, als
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden wol wiszentlichen sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchleuhtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, ewr hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gnadiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweisen wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen, daz in dieselb ir hab wider
                        oder aber gekeret werde, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
